bhop_strafe_m4chine is using :

sv_airaccelerate 100
sv_enablebunnyhopping 0

This map is a mostly a bhop map with some kz, longjump or ladders, its a real test for you strafes, map is not easy and only your good strafes can help you to finish it.

80% of the first part is multibhop, the 20% last % are once bhop.

Map is basicly made to be played on scroll!

good luck
